{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"What I thought I would do"},{"time":2000,"text":"is I would start with a simple request."},{"time":5000,"text":"I'd like all of you"},{"time":7000,"text":"to pause for a moment,"},{"time":9000,"text":"you wretched weaklings,"},{"time":11000,"text":"and take stock of your miserable existence."},{"time":14000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":18000,"text":"Now that was the advice"},{"time":20000,"text":"that St. Benedict gave his rather startled followers"},{"time":22000,"text":"in the fifth century."},{"time":24000,"text":"It was the advice that I decided to follow myself"},{"time":26000,"text":"when I turned 40."},{"time":29000,"text":"Up until that moment, I had been that classic corporate warrior --"},{"time":32000,"text":"I was eating too much, I was drinking too much,"},{"time":34000,"text":"I was working too hard"},{"time":36000,"text":"and I was neglecting the family."},{"time":38000,"text":"And I decided that I would try"},{"time":40000,"text":"and turn my life around."},{"time":42000,"text":"In particular, I decided"},{"time":44000,"text":"I would try to address the thorny issue"},{"time":46000,"text":"of work-life balance."},{"time":49000,"text":"So I stepped back from the workforce,"},{"time":52000,"text":"and I spent a year at home"},{"time":55000,"text":"with my wife and four young children."},{"time":58000,"text":"But all I learned about work-life balance"},{"time":60000,"text":"from that year"},{"time":62000,"text":"was that I found it quite easy"},{"time":64000,"text":"to balance work and life"},{"time":66000,"text":"when I didn't have any work."},{"time":68000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":72000,"text":"Not a very useful skill,"},{"time":74000,"text":"especially when the money runs out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77000,"text":"So I went back to work,"},{"time":79000,"text":"and I've spent these seven years since"},{"time":82000,"text":"struggling with, studying"},{"time":85000,"text":"and writing about work-life balance."},{"time":88000,"text":"And I have four observations"},{"time":90000,"text":"I'd like to share with you today."},{"time":92000,"text":"The first is:"},{"time":94000,"text":"if society's to make any progress on this issue,"},{"time":97000,"text":"we need an honest debate."},{"time":100000,"text":"But the trouble is"},{"time":102000,"text":"so many people talk so much rubbish"},{"time":104000,"text":"about work-life balance."},{"time":107000,"text":"All the discussions about flexi-time"},{"time":109000,"text":"or dress-down Fridays"},{"time":112000,"text":"or paternity leave"},{"time":114000,"text":"only serve to mask the core issue,"},{"time":117000,"text":"which is"},{"time":119000,"text":"that certain job and career choices"},{"time":122000,"text":"are fundamentally incompatible"},{"time":125000,"text":"with being meaningfully engaged"},{"time":127000,"text":"on a day-to-day basis"},{"time":129000,"text":"with a young family."},{"time":133000,"text":"Now the first step in solving any problem"},{"time":135000,"text":"is acknowledging the reality of the situation you're in."},{"time":138000,"text":"And the reality of the society that we're in"},{"time":142000,"text":"is there are thousands and thousands"},{"time":144000,"text":"of people out there"},{"time":146000,"text":"leading lives of quiet, screaming desperation,"},{"time":150000,"text":"where they work long, hard hours"},{"time":152000,"text":"at jobs they hate"},{"time":154000,"text":"to enable them to buy things they don't need"},{"time":156000,"text":"to impress people they don't like."},{"time":158000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":160000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":163000,"text":"It's my contention that going to work on Friday in jeans and [a] T-shirt"},{"time":167000,"text":"isn't really getting to the nub of the issue."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":173000,"text":"The second observation I'd like to make"},{"time":175000,"text":"is we need to face the truth"},{"time":177000,"text":"that governments and corporations"},{"time":179000,"text":"aren't going to solve this issue for us."},{"time":182000,"text":"We should stop looking outside."},{"time":184000,"text":"It's up to us as individuals"},{"time":186000,"text":"to take control and responsibility"},{"time":189000,"text":"for the type of lives that we want to lead."},{"time":192000,"text":"If you don't design your life,"},{"time":194000,"text":"someone else will design it for you,"},{"time":197000,"text":"and you may just not like"},{"time":199000,"text":"their idea of balance."},{"time":201000,"text":"It's particularly important --"},{"time":204000,"text":"this isn't on the World Wide Web, is it? I'm about to get fired --"},{"time":206000,"text":"it's particularly important"},{"time":208000,"text":"that you never put the quality of your life"},{"time":211000,"text":"in the hands of a commercial corporation."},{"time":215000,"text":"Now I'm not talking here just about the bad companies --"},{"time":218000,"text":"the \"abattoirs of the human soul,\" as I call them."},{"time":221000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":223000,"text":"I'm talking about all companies."},{"time":226000,"text":"Because commercial companies"},{"time":228000,"text":"are inherently designed"},{"time":230000,"text":"to get as much out of you [as]"},{"time":232000,"text":"they can get away with."},{"time":234000,"text":"It's in their nature; it's in their DNA;"},{"time":236000,"text":"it's what they do --"},{"time":238000,"text":"even the good, well-intentioned companies."},{"time":241000,"text":"On the one hand,"},{"time":243000,"text":"putting childcare facilities in the workplace"},{"time":245000,"text":"is wonderful and enlightened."},{"time":247000,"text":"On the other hand, it's a nightmare --"},{"time":249000,"text":"it just means you spend more time at the bloody office."},{"time":254000,"text":"We have to be responsible"},{"time":256000,"text":"for setting and enforcing"},{"time":258000,"text":"the boundaries that we want in our life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262000,"text":"The third observation is"},{"time":264000,"text":"we have to be careful"},{"time":266000,"text":"with the time frame that we choose"},{"time":269000,"text":"upon which to judge our balance."},{"time":273000,"text":"Before I went back to work"},{"time":275000,"text":"after my year at home,"},{"time":277000,"text":"I sat down"},{"time":279000,"text":"and I wrote out"},{"time":281000,"text":"a detailed, step-by-step description"},{"time":284000,"text":"of the ideal balanced day"},{"time":287000,"text":"that I aspired to."},{"time":289000,"text":"And it went like this:"},{"time":292000,"text":"wake up well rested"},{"time":294000,"text":"after a good night's sleep."},{"time":296000,"text":"Have sex."},{"time":299000,"text":"Walk the dog."},{"time":301000,"text":"Have breakfast with my wife and children."},{"time":304000,"text":"Have sex again."},{"time":306000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":309000,"text":"Drive the kids to school on the way to the office."},{"time":312000,"text":"Do three hours' work."},{"time":314000,"text":"Play a sport with a friend at lunchtime."},{"time":317000,"text":"Do another three hours' work."},{"time":319000,"text":"Meet some mates in the pub for an early evening drink."},{"time":323000,"text":"Drive home for dinner"},{"time":325000,"text":"with my wife and kids."},{"time":328000,"text":"Meditate for half an hour."},{"time":331000,"text":"Have sex."},{"time":333000,"text":"Walk the dog. Have sex again."},{"time":336000,"text":"Go to bed."},{"time":339000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":344000,"text":"How often do you think I have that day?"},{"time":346000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":349000,"text":"We need to be realistic."},{"time":351000,"text":"You can't do it all in one day."},{"time":353000,"text":"We need to elongate the time frame"},{"time":356000,"text":"upon which we judge the balance in our life,"},{"time":358000,"text":"but we need to elongate it"},{"time":360000,"text":"without falling into the trap"},{"time":362000,"text":"of the \"I'll have a life when I retire,"},{"time":365000,"text":"when my kids have left home,"},{"time":367000,"text":"when my wife has divorced me, my health is failing,"},{"time":370000,"text":"I've got no mates or interests left.\""},{"time":372000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":374000,"text":"A day is too short; \"after I retire\" is too long."},{"time":377000,"text":"There's got to be a middle way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381000,"text":"A fourth observation:"},{"time":383000,"text":"We need to approach balance"},{"time":385000,"text":"in a balanced way."},{"time":388000,"text":"A friend came to see me last year --"},{"time":390000,"text":"and she doesn't mind me telling this story -- a friend came to see me last year"},{"time":393000,"text":"and said, \"Nigel, I've read your book."},{"time":395000,"text":"And I realize that my life is completely out of balance."},{"time":398000,"text":"It's totally dominated by work."},{"time":401000,"text":"I work 10 hours a day; I commute two hours a day."},{"time":404000,"text":"All of my relationships have failed."},{"time":406000,"text":"There's nothing in my life"},{"time":408000,"text":"apart from my work."},{"time":410000,"text":"So I've decided to get a grip and sort it out."},{"time":413000,"text":"So I joined a gym.\""},{"time":415000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":418000,"text":"Now I don't mean to mock,"},{"time":421000,"text":"but being a fit 10-hour-a-day office rat"},{"time":425000,"text":"isn't more balanced; it's more fit."},{"time":428000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":430000,"text":"Lovely though physical exercise may be,"},{"time":433000,"text":"there are other parts to life --"},{"time":435000,"text":"there's the intellectual side; there's the emotional side;"},{"time":437000,"text":"there's the spiritual side."},{"time":439000,"text":"And to be balanced,"},{"time":441000,"text":"I believe we have to attend"},{"time":443000,"text":"to all of those areas --"},{"time":445000,"text":"not just do 50 stomach crunches."}]},{"cues":[{"time":448000,"text":"Now that can be daunting."},{"time":450000,"text":"Because people say, \"Bloody hell mate, I haven't got time to get fit."},{"time":453000,"text":"You want me to go to church and call my mother.\""},{"time":455000,"text":"And I understand."},{"time":457000,"text":"I truly understand how that can be daunting."},{"time":460000,"text":"But an incident that happened a couple of years ago"},{"time":463000,"text":"gave me a new perspective."},{"time":465000,"text":"My wife, who is somewhere in the audience today,"},{"time":468000,"text":"called me up at the office"},{"time":471000,"text":"and said, \"Nigel, you need to pick our youngest son\" --"},{"time":474000,"text":"Harry -- \"up from school.\""},{"time":476000,"text":"Because she had to be somewhere else with the other three children for that evening."},{"time":479000,"text":"So I left work an hour early that afternoon"},{"time":482000,"text":"and picked Harry up at the school gates."},{"time":486000,"text":"We walked down to the local park,"},{"time":488000,"text":"messed around on the swings, played some silly games."},{"time":491000,"text":"I then walked him up the hill to the local cafe,"},{"time":494000,"text":"and we shared a pizza for two,"},{"time":497000,"text":"then walked down the hill to our home,"},{"time":499000,"text":"and I gave him his bath"},{"time":501000,"text":"and put him in his Batman pajamas."},{"time":504000,"text":"I then read him a chapter"},{"time":506000,"text":"of Roald Dahl's \"James and the Giant Peach.\""},{"time":509000,"text":"I then put him to bed, tucked him in,"},{"time":511000,"text":"gave him a kiss on his forehead and said, \"Goodnight, mate,\""},{"time":513000,"text":"and walked out of his bedroom."},{"time":515000,"text":"As I was walking out of his bedroom,"},{"time":517000,"text":"he said, \"Dad?\" I went, \"Yes, mate?\""},{"time":520000,"text":"He went, \"Dad, this has been the best day"},{"time":522000,"text":"of my life, ever.\""},{"time":527000,"text":"I hadn't done anything,"},{"time":530000,"text":"hadn't taken him to Disney World or bought him a Playstation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":533000,"text":"Now my point is"},{"time":535000,"text":"the small things matter."},{"time":538000,"text":"Being more balanced"},{"time":540000,"text":"doesn't mean dramatic upheaval in your life."},{"time":543000,"text":"With the smallest investment"},{"time":545000,"text":"in the right places,"},{"time":547000,"text":"you can radically transform the quality of your relationships"},{"time":550000,"text":"and the quality of your life."},{"time":552000,"text":"Moreover, I think,"},{"time":554000,"text":"it can transform society."},{"time":557000,"text":"Because if enough people do it,"},{"time":559000,"text":"we can change society's definition of success"},{"time":562000,"text":"away from the moronically simplistic notion"},{"time":565000,"text":"that the person with the most money when he dies wins,"},{"time":569000,"text":"to a more thoughtful and balanced definition"},{"time":572000,"text":"of what a life well lived looks like."},{"time":576000,"text":"And that, I think,"},{"time":578000,"text":"is an idea worth spreading."}]},{"cues":[{"time":580000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}